Package: ShinyLocalEdu
Type: Package
Title: Local Shiny Apps for Statistics Education
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-05-28
Author: HomerWhite <hwhite0@georgetowncollege.edu>
Maintainer: HomerWhite <hwhite0@georgetowncollege.edu>
Description: A set of wrapper-functions for locally-run Shiny apps.
    Users can easily load their own data into the app for exploration:
    no hassle with uploading csv files to a remote web-app, etc.
Depends:
    shiny (>= 0.11)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    lattice,
    shinythemes
Suggests:
    knitr
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: TRUE
VignetteBuilder: knitr
